              <tr> 
                <td class="chblue"><font class="h1font"> Advanced Decks</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="3"><tr><td><font class="bfont"><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td colspan="2"><font class="h1font">The Talon Strikes Back</font></td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Rating</Font></TD><TD><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><font size=1>(4.27)</font> | <A HREF="/magination/decks/decks.php?reviews=21555">Read Reviews</A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Author</font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> <A HREF="http://www.decktech.net/magination/main/mpage.php?member=6010">Andrew "cfbnv" Harwell</A></FONT> <font class="afont"> <a href='http://www.decktech.net/magination/main/mpage.php?member=6010&sub=1'> (Subscribe to this member)</a></font></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Description</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> Rethought, revamped, and completely redone, this is a more consistent version of the Cataclysmasaurus combo that is sure to get what it needs to win.</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Submitted</Font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> February 19, 2002</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Cards</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> Magi:<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(528)">Sorreah</a><br>
(Starting: <a href="javascript:card_browser(669)">Cataclysm</a>, Cataclsym or <a href="javascript:card_browser(355)">Shockwave</a>)<br>
<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(527)">Kalius</a><br>
(Starting: <a href="javascript:card_browser(356)">Shooting Star</a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(524)">Warlum</a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(520)">Flutter Yup</a>)<br>
<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(573)">Harror</a><br>
(Starting: <a href="javascript:card_browser(594)">Shryque</a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(585)">Dark <a href="javascript:card_browser(325)">Ayebaw</a></a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(669)">Cataclysm</a>)<br>
<br>
Creatures (28)<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(325)">Ayebaw</a> - 3<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(585)">Dark <a href="javascript:card_browser(325)">Ayebaw</a></a> - 3<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(522)">Night Hyren</a> - 2<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(520)">Flutter Yup</a> - 2<br>
